@startuml Composite Structure Diagram - AIProcessor
!theme cerulean-outline

title SmartMedia - Composite Structure Diagram (AIProcessor Internal Architecture)

package "AIProcessor (SmartMediaEngine)" {
  component [AIProcessor] {
    
    ' Internal parts/components
    interface "ImageInput" as img_input <<Port>> {
      + imageTensor: Tensor[T, H, W, 3]
      + metadata: dict
    }
    
    interface "TextInput" as txt_input <<Port>> {
      + prompt: string
      + max_tokens: int
    }
    
    interface "TextOutput" as txt_output <<Port>> {
      + tokens: List<str>
      + embeddings: ndarray[1536]
      + logits: Tensor
    }
    
    interface "FaceOutput" as face_output <<Port>> {
      + face_ids: List<str>
      + encodings: ndarray[128]
      + locations: List[Bbox]
    }
    
    ' Internal parts
    component [Tokenizer] {
      + tokenize(text: str): List[int]
      + detokenize(ids: List[int]): str
      + vocab_size: 151646
      + max_sequence_length: 8192
    }
    
    component [VisionEncoder] {
      + forward(images: Tensor) -> Tensor
      + patch_size: 14
      + hidden_dim: 1024
      + num_layers: 24
      + attention_heads: 16
      + supported_formats: [jpg, png, heic, webp]
      + max_image_size: 256 (optimized)
    }
    
    component [PositionalEncoding] {
      + encode_patches()
      + m_rope() : rotary embeddings
      + temporal_position()
      + spatial_grid()
    }
    
    component [CrossAttentionBridge] {
      + q_proj: Linear[hidden_dim -> attn_dim]
      + k_proj: Linear[hidden_dim -> attn_dim]
      + v_proj: Linear[hidden_dim -> attn_dim]
      + attention_heads: 16
      + dropout: 0.1
    }
    
    component [LLMHead] {
      + transformer_layers: 24
      + hidden_dim: 2048
      + intermediate_dim: 8192
      + dropout: 0.1
      + forward(x: Tensor, cross_attn: Tensor) -> Tensor
      + generate(max_new_tokens: int) -> List<str>
    }
    
    component [EmbeddingLayer] {
      + embed(tokens: List[int]) -> Tensor
      + embed_text(text: str) -> ndarray[1536]
      + model: sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2
      + normalize: true
    }
    
    component [FaceDetector] {
      + detect(image: ndarray) -> List[Face]
      + model: face_recognition library
      + upsample_num_times: 0 (fast mode)
      + detection_model: hog
      + encoding_model: small (128-dim)
    }
    
    component [OutputDecoder] {
      + decode_tokens(token_ids: List[int]) -> str
      + parse_objects(text: str) -> List[str]
      + parse_emotion(text: str) -> str
      + parse_scene(text: str) -> str
      + parse_colors(text: str) -> List[str]
    }
    
    ' Internal bus/connectors
    component [EmbeddingBus] {
      + dimension: 1536
      + batch_size: 1
      + device: cuda/cpu
    }
    
    component [AttentionCrossbar] {
      + q: Tensor[seq_len, attn_dim]
      + k: Tensor[seq_len, attn_dim]
      + v: Tensor[seq_len, attn_dim]
      + attention_scores: softmax(q·k^T/√d)
    }
    
    ' Connectors showing data flow
    img_input --> VisionEncoder : "Tensor[1, 3, 256, 256]"
    txt_input --> Tokenizer : "string query"
    
    VisionEncoder --> PositionalEncoding : "patch embeddings"
    PositionalEncoding --> CrossAttentionBridge : "positioned encoder output"
    
    Tokenizer --> LLMHead : "token embeddings"
    CrossAttentionBridge --> AttentionCrossbar : "cross-attention\nqueries/keys/values"
    
    AttentionCrossbar --> LLMHead : "attended context"
    LLMHead --> OutputDecoder : "logits"
    
    OutputDecoder --> txt_output : "decoded tokens\n+ metadata"
    
    VisionEncoder --> EmbeddingLayer : "visual features"
    EmbeddingLayer --> EmbeddingBus : "1536-dim vectors"
    EmbeddingBus --> txt_output : "embeddings for FAISS"
    
    VisionEncoder --> FaceDetector : "image tensor"
    FaceDetector --> face_output : "face encodings"
    
  }
}

' External connections
[AIProcessor] : "Get Image" ..> img_input
[AIProcessor] : "Get Prompt" ..> txt_input
[AIProcessor] : "Return Text" ..> txt_output
[AIProcessor] : "Return Faces" ..> face_output

note right of VisionEncoder
  **Qwen2-VL Vision Encoder**
  • Optimized for 256x256 (fast)
  • Patch-based tokenization
  • 24 transformer layers
  • Multi-head attention
end note

note right of LLMHead
  **Large Language Model Head**
  • 24 transformer layers
  • 2048 hidden dimension
  • Causal self-attention
  • Cross-attention with vision
  • max_new_tokens: 85 (optimized)
end note

note right of CrossAttentionBridge
  **Vision-Language Fusion**
  • Connects encoder to LLM
  • Rotary Positional Embedding (M-ROPE)
  • Multiple alignment heads
  • Low-rank adaptation possible
end note

note right of EmbeddingLayer
  **Semantic Vector Generation**
  • Sentence Transformers
  • 1536-dimensional output
  • L2 normalized
  • Used for FAISS indexing
end note

note right of FaceDetector
  **Face Recognition Module**
  • Fast HOG detector (not CNN)
  • 128-dim face encodings
  • Cosine similarity matching
  • Fast clustering ready
end note

note bottom of "AIProcessor (SmartMediaEngine)"
  **Processing Pipeline Performance**
  • Image Load: ~20ms
  • Vision Encoding: ~200ms (GPU)
  • LLM Generation: ~1500ms (GPU)
  • Embedding: ~50ms
  • Face Detection: ~100ms
  • Total: ~2sec per image (optimized)
end note

@enduml
